fulltitle: Preview: Inside The Studios - James Newton Howard
description:
Early in April of 2017 I had an amazing opportunity to meet one of the best film composer of all time; James Newton Howard. He allowed me to use my camera and record his talk. 🎬

I was so busy working on myself for the rest of the year, that I had literally no time to even go back and listen to his talk again. 💪 Now before Christmas, I decided I want to share a little bit of what he taught me with you! Stay tuned! 🎧 🎵
